    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. Mechanically, it is very sound, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has received regular oil changes. The interior is clean with only minor signs of wear on the driver's seat, and all electronic features, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. While the exterior paint retains a nice shine, there are a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scratch on the rear bumper consistent with normal use. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
