    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs, some paint fading on the hood, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear, and the air conditioning takes a moment to get cold. While it runs and drives safely, a buyer should expect to invest in some minor mechanical maintenance and cosmetic detailing in the near future.",
