    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. The exterior maintains a refined finish, while the interior reflects a high standard of stewardship. A premier selection for the professional seeking a dependable, high-value investment that delivers a superior driving experience.",
