      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, with only minor, expected stone chips on the front fascia from highway commuting and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the high-resolution infotainment screen to the heated seats\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, and I have a comprehensive folder of service receipts to prove it. Most recently, it underwent a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection that confirmed the suspension and drivetrain are in great shape. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced just last year. This is a non-smoker vehicle with a clean title and no history of accidents, offering a reliable and premium driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
